{"tid":440473,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚] 有冇劇情小品遊戲推薦","createTime":"2017-10-18T20:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T09:15:10.000Z","uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"985259688a5e74ddd08644826260155e460bf00f","tid":440473,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T20:38:46.000Z","msg":"玩厭左抽抽刷刷 日日定時定候做任務 無限loop既手機game<br />\n<br />\n呢排機緣巧合down左隻叫 Opus: Rocket of Whispers, 台灣人整既, 出左一個月左右 (唔做打手介紹, 有興趣自己search)<br />\n<br />\n雖然好快爆機 不過劇情同配樂係手機game黎講都做得幾高質 畫風可能有人唔鍾意 遊戲節奏都偏慢 不過我覺得幾舒服, 又有d感動位 訓唔著開黎玩下幾好 (玩晒成個故事要俾15蚊,不過我覺得抵俾)<br />\n<br />\n有冇人都有玩過 或者有冇差唔多玩法/風格既game推薦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0125699522b548f15b2774205873b766b7384d","tid":440473,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T03:11:31.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"9921dc04eb4420cafe800691e9ceccbccd19939a","tid":440473,"uid":479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T03:12:06.000Z","msg":"屌樓主老母"},{"pid":"7298d272fa4f5450e104ced3e09d63041b2bac40","tid":440473,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T23:30:38.000Z","msg":"Opus仲有前作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDeemo 劇情向音game 睇下有冇興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39527cbe3cc14ec28d1c5eab0866b4cee0f50bdc","tid":440473,"uid":24465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-24T23:34:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Opus仲有前作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDeemo 劇情向音game 睇下有冇興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYear Walk 都ok （唔）恐怖解謎遊戲<br />\n唔溫馨又短 不過劇情都唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d60ea6511cec893653400865860a5436311f3d73","tid":440473,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T09:15:10